{"tid":1070921,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【5毛召喚】特朗普：擬維持對華貨關稅「一段長時間」","createTime":"2019-03-21T04:08:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-21T04:30:43.000Z","uid":54373,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"cd8ce54da7bc77ae0b52e2c496967c17b80c0166","tid":1070921,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T04:08:58.000Z","msg":"【新增影片】 美國總統特朗普周三表示，中美貿易談判進展良好，但表示政府正討論維持對中國貨的關稅「一段長時間」。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普周三前往俄亥俄州前，在白宮回應記者提問，表示維持關稅可確保中國遵守協議。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普曾表示，關稅的威脅可令北京尋求達成協議之心更切。<br />\n<br />\n美國周二表示，中美下周會展開新一輪高級別貿易談判，美國貿易代表萊特希澤和財長姆努欽（Steven Mnuchin）下周會到北京。《華爾街日報》（WSJ）報道，中方首席談判代表、副總理劉鶴下月第一周則會去華盛頓。雙方希望最遲下月達成貿易協議。<br />\n<br />\n談判其中一個關鍵議題是執行機制，美國想保留向中國貨品加徵關稅的選項，並希望中國不報復。<br />\n<br />\n路透社／美聯社"},{"pid":"33a85b5d15767b759540eb0cd829e8b5daac9dca","tid":1070921,"uid":7369,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T04:13:33.000Z","msg":"美中和好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"028cb82df06da4e997f8fa2a182dff731e9f493b","tid":1070921,"uid":99856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T04:14:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7a858015c6e9df6cd0367a005d93eb91f23dbde","tid":1070921,"uid":54381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"33a85b5d15767b759540eb0cd829e8b5daac9dca","tid":1070921,"uid":7369,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T04:13:33.000Z","msg":"美中和好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T04:16:30.000Z","msg":"反中撚炒晒車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5daa4d147d889434c31d94174ecf12b767052bc","tid":1070921,"uid":11148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T04:23:54.000Z","msg":"回憶賤種呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94ba7755b4ec3658d93f9c9092ea490f4326bc98","tid":1070921,"uid":